<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/veterans-advisory-and-pensions-committees-x13> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "We serve and support ex-servicemen and women, their widows or widowers and their immediate family members. We are an independent voice, here to help you whenever or wherever you served, whether in World War 2 or Afghanistan. VAPC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Defence ."@en .
